  Package: %N-dev
  Depends: %N-shlibs (=%v-%r), x11
  Replaces: %N (<< 1.0.1-4)
  Files: include lib/lib*-1.0.* lib/pkgconfig share/gtk-doc
  DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog NEWS README TODO
<<
